BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-21T03:30:00&endDate=2026-06-22T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nELIZABETH LINE: Sunday 21 June\, no service between Paddington and Abbey Wood / Stratford. Trains operate between Paddington National Rail Station and Heathrow / Reading\, and between Liverpool Street National Rail Station and Gidea Park / Shenfield.
